PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781100698
OL,3,CFive arrested and more than #30m of
OL,4,Ccocaine recovered in at-sea smuggling
OL,5,Cbid
OL,7,FMore than #30m of cocaine has been
OL,8,Fdiscovered on a boat in Eastbourne by
OL,9,Finvestigators.
OL,11,FOfficers from the National Crime
OL,12,FAgency (NCA) seized 425kg of the Class
OL,13,FA drug from a fishing vessel at
OL,14,FEastbourne Marina just after 1pm on
OL,15,FMonday (8 June).
OL,17,FIt's thought the cocaine has a street
OL,18,Fvalue of #34m.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
