OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781100698
OL,3,CFive arrested and more than #30m of
OL,4,Ccocaine recovered in at-sea smuggling
OL,5,Cbid
OL,7,FA total of five people have been
OL,8,Farrested in connection with the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FIt's alleged four of the men picked up
OL,12,Fthe drugs using a fishing vessel
OL,13,Fcalled New Horizon, after they were
OL,14,Fdropped in the English Channel by
OL,15,Fanother boat, before returning to
OL,16,Fshore.
OL,18,FThe fifth man was not on the vessel
OL,19,Fand was arrested when the other four
OL,20,Freturned to harbour.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781100698
OL,3,CFive arrested and more than #30m of
OL,4,Ccocaine recovered in at-sea smuggling
OL,5,Cbid
OL,7,FThe men, aged 32 to 49, are from
OL,8,FScotland and Eastbourne. They remain
OL,9,Fin custody at this time.
OL,11,FThe operation was carried out by the
OL,12,FNCA's Maritime, Aviation and Military
OL,13,FIntervention Cell, the Joint Maritime
OL,14,FSecurity Centre, Sussex Police and
OL,15,FPolice Scotland.
OL,17,FA number of searches have also been
OL,18,Fcarried out in Scotland.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781100698
OL,3,CFive arrested and more than #30m of
OL,4,Ccocaine recovered in at-sea smuggling
OL,5,Cbid
OL,7,FCarl Barrass, NCA senior investigating
OL,8,Fofficer, said: "The recovery of this
OL,9,Fquantity of cocaine represents a
OL,10,Fsignificant loss to the organised
OL,11,Fcrime group behind its importation and
OL,12,Fwill impact its ability to continue
OL,13,Foperating.
OL,15,F"Combating the threat of Class A drugs
OL,16,Fis a priority for the NCA and we will
OL,17,Fcontinue to work with partners at home
OL,18,Fand abroad to protect the public."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
